{#- BEYOND → prose -#}
<section class="sec reveal" id="acct-cashflow-beyond">
  <div class="ct read read--doc">
    <div class="idx"><span class="idx__n">§</span><span class="idx__t">Beyond the forecast</span><span class="idx__rule"></span></div>
    <h2 class="h2" style="margin-bottom:16px;">When cash is under control, the bigger questions open up.</h2>
    <div class="prose">
      <p>A reliable forecast does more than prevent shortfalls &mdash; it changes what you can plan. Once you can see cash clearly, you can decide when to hire, whether to expand, how to price for margin, and how much you can safely invest in growth. That&rsquo;s the natural step from managing cash to steering the business.</p>
      <p>For businesses that want that judgment on an ongoing basis, a <strong>fractional CFO</strong> takes cash management as one piece of a broader seat &mdash; forecasting, KPIs, strategy, and board-level reporting. As automation handles the routine, this is where the real value now lives. <a href="/accounting/advisory/fractional-cfo/?intent=fractional-cfo">Explore fractional CFO &amp; advisory <svg width="15" height="15" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.75" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M4 12h15M13 6l6 6-6 6" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/></svg></a></p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

